snippet.title: Unbuild Announcement
snippet.description:
Build turrets the other way around! 
Here you have 10 completed building block constructs. 
Can you take it brick by brick 
without anything falling to the ground?

Which stone you can take away 
determined by chance!

Have fun dismantling! 

arrives for mobile devices and itch.io

on April 28, 2021

https://klickaffen.tv/unbuild
